relasikan ke db_product_description
-product_id
-name
-description

relasikan ke db_category_sandbox dan buatkan 3 level category
-category_id
-parent_id

berikut contoh pembuatan level category nya
Struktur Tabel Category
Tabel yang digunakan: DbCategorySandbox

Kolom Utama:
category_id - ID kategori (Primary Key)
parent_id - ID parent kategori (0 untuk root/level 0)
name - Nama kategori
slug - URL-friendly string
status - Status aktif/tidak (1/0)
Alur Category 3 Level di findOne()
1. Penentuan Level Kategori
2. Proses Identifikasi Level
let categoryLevel = 0;
let parentCategory = null;
let grandParentCategory = null;

if (currentCategory.parent_id !== 0) {
    // Get parent category
    parentCategory = await models.DbCategorySandbox.findOne({
        where: { category_id: currentCategory.parent_id }
    });

    if (parentCategory) {
        if (parentCategory.parent_id === 0) {
            categoryLevel = 1; // Current adalah child
        } else {
            categoryLevel = 2; // Current adalah grandchild
            
            // Get grandparent category
            grandParentCategory = await models.DbCategorySandbox.findOne({
                where: { category_id: parentCategory.parent_id }
            });
        }
    }
}
3. Struktur Data Response Berdasarkan Level
Level 0 (Root Category)
categoryInfo = {
    category: {
        value: currentCategory.category_id.toString(),
        parentId: "0",
        name: currentCategory.name,
        slug: currentCategory.slug,
    }
};
Level 1 (Child Category)
categoryInfo = {
    category: {
        value: parentCategory.category_id.toString(),
        parentId: "0",
        name: parentCategory.name,
        slug: parentCategory.slug,
    },
    categoryChildren: categoryChildren.map((child) => ({
        value: child.value,
        parentId: child.parentId,
        name: child.name,
        slug: child.slug,
        isSelected: parseInt(child.value) === dataValues.category_id,
    })),
};
Level 2 (Grandchild Category) - 3 Level Hierarchy
categoryInfo = {
    // Level 0 - Grandparent
    category: {
        value: grandParentCategory.category_id.toString(),
        parentId: "0",
        name: grandParentCategory.name,
        slug: grandParentCategory.slug,
    },
    // Level 1 - Parent's siblings
    categoryChildren: categoryChildren.map((child) => ({
        value: child.value,
        parentId: child.parentId,
        name: child.name,
        slug: child.slug,
        isSelected: parseInt(child.value) === parentCategory.category_id,
    })),
    // Level 2 - Current level's siblings
    grandCategoryChildren: grandCategoryChildren.map((grandChild) => ({
        value: grandChild.value,
        parentId: grandChild.parentId,
        name: grandChild.name,
        slug: grandChild.slug,
        isSelected: parseInt(grandChild.value) === dataValues.category_id,
    })),
};
Helper Method untuk Get Children
async buildGrandCategoryChildren(categoryId) {
    // Get semua child categories dengan parent_id = categoryId
    const grandChildren = await models.DbCategorySandbox.findAll({
        where: {
            parent_id: categoryId,
            status: 1, // Hanya kategori aktif
        },
        attributes: ["category_id", "parent_id", "name", "slug"],
        order: [["name", "ASC"]],
    });

    return grandChildren.map((child) => ({
        value: child.category_id.toString(),
        parentId: child.parent_id.toString(),
        name: child.name,
        slug: child.slug,
    }));
}
Contoh Hierarchy
Level 0 (Root):     Elektronik (id: 1, parent_id: 0)
                           |
Level 1 (Child):    Komputer (id: 2, parent_id: 1)
                           |
Level 2 (Grandchild): Laptop (id: 3, parent_id: 2)

Flow Diagram
Product.category_id = 3 (Laptop)
    ↓
1. Get currentCategory (Laptop, parent_id=2)
    ↓
2. parent_id != 0, get parentCategory (Komputer, parent_id=1)
    ↓
3. parentCategory.parent_id != 0, set categoryLevel=2
    ↓
4. Get grandParentCategory (Elektronik, parent_id=0)
    ↓
5. Get categoryChildren (siblings of Komputer under Elektronik)
    ↓
6. Get grandCategoryChildren (siblings of Laptop under Komputer)
    ↓
7. Build response dengan 3 level hierarchy